---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { siteConfig } from '../config/site';
---

<Base title="Terms of Service">
  <article class="flex-1 px-6 py-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-foreground mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-sm max-w-none space-y-6 text-foreground/80">
      <p class="text-foreground/60 text-sm">
        Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { month: 'long', year: 'numeric' })}
      </p>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>
          By using {siteConfig.name}, you agree to these Terms of Service and TailTag's safety
          policies. If you do not agree, please do not use the app.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">Description of Service</h2>
        <p>
          {siteConfig.name} is a mobile game for fursuit enthusiasts at conventions. Users can register
          fursuits, log catches in the app, and track achievements and statistics.
        </p>
        <p>
          TailTag is intended for users who are at least 13 years old. TailTag is not a dating,
          matchmaking, hookup, random chat, or adult-content service.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">User Content And Conduct</h2>
        <p>
          TailTag includes user-generated profiles, fursuit listings, photos, catch submissions,
          report text, and other user-provided content. You agree to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mt-2">
          <li>Provide accurate information about yourself and your fursuit(s)</li>
          <li>Respect other users and their privacy</li>
          <li>Not upload adult, sexual, pornographic, offensive, or illegal content</li>
          <li>
            Not use TailTag for dating, matchmaking, hookup, or sexually explicit interactions
          </li>
          <li>Not harass, bully, threaten, abuse, impersonate, or exploit other users</li>
          <li>
            Not groom, coerce, sexualize, exploit, endanger, or seek sexual contact with minors
          </li>
          <li>
            Not request, link to, create, upload, or distribute child sexual abuse material (CSAM)
            or child sexual abuse and exploitation (CSAE)
          </li>
          <li>Not attempt to exploit, hack, or disrupt the service</li>
          <li>Only log catches and share information with other users' consent</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">18+ Visibility</h2>
        <p>
          TailTag may allow users who confirm they are 18 or older to limit profile or fursuit
          visibility to other users who have also confirmed they are 18 or older. This is a privacy
          and visibility setting only. It does not allow adult, sexual, pornographic, dating,
          matchmaking, hookup, or otherwise prohibited content or conduct.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">Reporting And Blocking</h2>
        <p>
          Users can report profiles, fursuits, and catch content inside TailTag. Users can also
          block other users. TailTag staff may review reports, remove content, restrict features,
          suspend accounts, or take other action when content or behavior violates these terms or
          TailTag's safety policies.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">Content Ownership</h2>
        <p>
          You retain ownership of photos and content you upload. By uploading, you grant {
            siteConfig.name
          } a license to display this content within the app to other users.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">Account Termination</h2>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to suspend or terminate accounts that violate these terms. You may
          delete your account at any time through the app settings.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          {siteConfig.name} is provided for entertainment purposes. We are not liable for any damages
          arising from use of the service.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For questions about these terms, email{' '}
          <a
            href={`mailto:${siteConfig.links.supportEmail}`}
            class="text-primary hover:underline"
            >{siteConfig.links.supportEmail}</a
          >.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
  <Footer />
</Base>
